order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">owns titles</a> includi=
ng TheStreet, Parade and Men=E2=80=99s Journal. Since 2019, it has also pub=
lished Sports Illustrated, though it doesn=E2=80=99t own it: The Sports Ill=
