 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">acquired it in 2019</a> and then licensed it to Arena fo=
r 10 years.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color:=
