ackground-color: #ccc;">come up around here before</a>. B. Riley also owned=
 most of Arena=E2=80=99s debt, in the form of=C2=A0$110 million of bonds.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And then in August Arena <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34098266.257404/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmd=
vdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzg5NDg3MS8wMDAxNDkzMTUyMjMwMjg1MDgvZXg5OS0yLm=
