ion of cash, and commit to buy $60 million worth of advertising over five y=
ears for =E2=80=9Ca group of consumer brands also owned by Simplify, includ=
ing 5-hour ENERGY.=E2=80=9D In exchange for the assets, cash and advertisin=
g, Bhargava would get control of Arena.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On Nov. 5, they <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/34098266.257404/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9k=
